Homepage: http://uni.bodz.net/net/netcaps
Vcs-Git: git://git.bodz.net/uni.git
Vcs-Browser: http://git.bodz.net/uni/net/netcaps

Package: netcaps
Architecture: any
Depends: 
    bash-shlib,
    libbas-d,
    tcpdump,
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: Network capturing and analysis tools
    This package contains some tools for network capturing and analysis.
    These tools are mainly based on tcpdump/tcpflow.
    You can find alternatives for some famous programs like urlsnarf.
Description-zh_CN: 网络捕捉与分析综合工具集
    这个软件包是一些用于网络数据包的捕捉与分析的工具。
    这些工具主要构建于 tcpdump/tcpflow 之上。
    一些经典的程序如 urlsnarf 在这个软件包中都有重写的替代版本。
